---
title: Hearty Beef and Garden Vegetable Soup with Cheesy Garlic Bread
description: Nothing says cooler weather than a bowl of soup! Hearty and packed with veggies, this soup will warm from the inside out. The garlic cheese toasts are perfect dippers.
